text:
Loudest scream = Barcelona & Paris
Biggest crowd = Jakarta
The idea of white ocean = Kaohsiung
So what's so special about Manila that BP treats them more than their other tours?

One of their European tours, during soundcheck, Blinks asked them to sing Ice cream but were ignored. In Jakarta, BLINKS' screams were very clear asking them to sing Boombayah as the closing concert, once again being ignored. But all that is not for Manila.
We envy? No! We were disappointed. We all deserve a concert of the same quality, for the price of the tickets we buy. 💔💔💔🤔🤔🤔😏😏😏
